{"generated":"2026-04-27T20:57:15.103876+00:00","period_start":"2026-04-21T02:31:00+00:00","period_end":"2026-04-27T19:24:00+00:00","snapshot_count":27,"html":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n<title>The Vendetta Gazette – May 4, 1926</title>\n<style>\n  body { font-family: Georgia, serif; background: #f5ecd7; color: #1a1a1a; max-width: 860px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }\n  h1 { text-align: center; font-size: 2.8em; letter-spacing: 4px; text-transform: uppercase; border-top: 6px double #1a1a1a; border-bottom: 6px double #1a1a1a; padding: 10px 0; margin-bottom: 4px; }\n  h2 { text-align: center; font-size: 1em; letter-spacing: 2px; margin-top: 2px; margin-bottom: 16px; }\n  h3 { font-size: 1.35em; text-transform: uppercase; border-bottom: 2px solid #1a1a1a; margin-top: 24px; }\n  p { line-height: 1.75; margin: 10px 0; text-align: justify; }\n  blockquote { background: #e8d9b5; border: 3px double #1a1a1a; margin: 20px 0; padding: 16px 20px; font-style: italic; }\n  blockquote strong { display: block; font-style: normal; font-size: 1.1em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #1a1a1a; padding-bottom: 4px; }\n  hr { border: none; border-top: 3px double #1a1a1a; margin: 28px 0; }\n  .subhead { font-style: italic; font-size: 1.05em; display: block; margin-top: -6px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #444; }\n  .byline { font-size: 0.85em; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 2px; color: #555; margin-bottom: 16px; display: block; }\n  .leaderboard { background: #1a1a1a; color: #f5ecd7; padding: 12px 18px; margin: 16px 0; font-family: 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 0.92em; }\n  .leaderboard strong { display: block; text-align: center; font-size: 1.1em; letter-spacing: 2px; margin-bottom: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #f5ecd7; padding-bottom: 4px; }\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n<h1>The Vendetta Gazette</h1>\n<h2>Special Edition &bull; May 4, 2026 &bull; &ldquo;All the Blood That&rsquo;s Fit to Print&rdquo; &bull; Two Cents (If You&rsquo;re Still Alive to Pay)</h2>\n\n<hr>\n<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"640\" height=\"248\" style=\"font-family:Georgia,serif;background:#0a0800;display:block;margin:18px auto\">\n<text x=\"320\" y=\"22\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#c8a84a\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"bold\" letter-spacing=\"2\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">TERRITORY GAINS THIS WEEK</text>\n<line x1=\"20\" y1=\"28\" x2=\"620\" y2=\"28\" stroke=\"#3a2a00\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n<text x=\"154\" y=\"48\" text-anchor=\"end\" fill=\"#a09060\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">Donald Trump</text>\n<rect x=\"160\" y=\"35\" width=\"400\" height=\"16\" fill=\"#c8a84a\" opacity=\"0.85\"/>\n<text x=\"566\" y=\"48\" fill=\"#c8a84a\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">+45</text>\n<text x=\"154\" y=\"76\" text-anchor=\"end\" fill=\"#a09060\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">Wu-Tang</text>\n<rect x=\"160\" y=\"63\" width=\"257\" height=\"16\" fill=\"#c8a84a\" opacity=\"0.85\"/>\n<text x=\"423\" y=\"76\" fill=\"#c8a84a\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">+29</text>\n<text x=\"154\" y=\"104\" text-anchor=\"end\" fill=\"#a09060\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">Cokro</text>\n<rect x=\"160\" y=\"91\" width=\"186\" height=\"16\" fill=\"#c8a84a\" opacity=\"0.85\"/>\n<text x=\"352\" y=\"104\" fill=\"#c8a84a\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">+21</text>\n<text x=\"154\" y=\"132\" text-anchor=\"end\" fill=\"#a09060\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">Blood Captain</text>\n<rect x=\"160\" y=\"119\" width=\"62\" height=\"16\" fill=\"#c8a84a\" opacity=\"0.85\"/>\n<text x=\"228\" y=\"132\" fill=\"#c8a84a\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">+7</text>\n<text x=\"154\" y=\"160\" text-anchor=\"end\" fill=\"#a09060\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">huzi manor</text>\n<rect x=\"160\" y=\"147\" width=\"62\" height=\"16\" fill=\"#c8a84a\" opacity=\"0.85\"/>\n<text x=\"228\" y=\"160\" fill=\"#c8a84a\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">+7</text>\n<text x=\"154\" y=\"188\" text-anchor=\"end\" fill=\"#a09060\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">chiavenna</text>\n<rect x=\"160\" y=\"175\" width=\"53\" height=\"16\" fill=\"#c8a84a\" opacity=\"0.85\"/>\n<text x=\"219\" y=\"188\" fill=\"#c8a84a\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">+6</text>\n<text x=\"154\" y=\"216\" text-anchor=\"end\" fill=\"#a09060\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">Fyh</text>\n<rect x=\"160\" y=\"203\" width=\"8\" height=\"16\" fill=\"#c8a84a\" opacity=\"0.85\"/>\n<text x=\"174\" y=\"216\" fill=\"#c8a84a\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">+1</text>\n</svg>\n\n\n<h3>TRUMP'S REIGN OF GOLD CONTINUES — AND LAKHHE PAYS THE ULTIMATE PRICE!</h3>\n<span class=\"subhead\">Platinum Pompadour Completes the Most Savage Elimination in Vendetta City History — Six Headquarters Shattered, One Man Left with Nothing but Memories</span>\n<span class=\"byline\">By Our Man in the Trenches, Ignatius P. Flambeau</span>\n\n<p>Sweet mother of all that is holy and several things that decidedly are not — <strong>Donald Trump</strong>, the self-proclaimed Golden Emperor of Vendetta City, has once again made the city's other bosses look like schoolboys playing marbles in the gutter! Faithful readers, you will recall from our previous breathless dispatch that the Platinum Pompadour had already commenced his systematic dismantling of the hapless <strong>Lakhhe</strong>. Well, citizens, that demolition job is now <em>complete.</em></p>\n\n<p>This week — spanning April 21st through the blood-drenched evening of April 27th — Trump stormed Lakhhe's headquarters on April 21st, 22nd, 24th, and an absolutely <em>unconscionable</em> triple-header on the 25th. Six headquarters captures in total. Six! When the dust finally settled, Lakhhe's once-proud 26-turf empire had been stripped to the bone and its proprietor sent packing into the cold night air with nothing but his XP and his wounded pride. Eliminated, finished, done — as completely as last Tuesday's bootleg gin supply!</p>\n\n<p>And if six headquarters captures weren't sufficient to slake his golden thirst, Trump also dispatched the mysterious operator known only as <strong>404</strong> on April 26th — a man whose very name suggested he could not be found, yet somehow was found repeatedly, captured, and sent to whatever digital oblivion awaits the eliminated. For the week, Trump seized <strong>45 fresh territories</strong> through 28 relentless territorial assaults, while simultaneously swelling his private army by a jaw-dropping <strong>361 new gangsters</strong>, bringing his fearsome garrison to a staggering 4,978 battle-hardened souls. The man isn't merely winning — he's <em>building a monument to winning.</em></p>\n\n<hr>\n<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"640\" height=\"276\" style=\"font-family:Georgia,serif;background:#0a0800;display:block;margin:18px auto\">\n<text x=\"320\" y=\"22\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#c8a84a\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"bold\" letter-spacing=\"2\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">HEAVIEST LOSSES THIS WEEK</text>\n<line x1=\"20\" y1=\"28\" x2=\"620\" y2=\"28\" stroke=\"#3a2a00\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n<text x=\"154\" y=\"48\" text-anchor=\"end\" fill=\"#a09060\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">Lakhhe</text>\n<rect x=\"160\" y=\"35\" width=\"400\" height=\"16\" fill=\"#8b1a1a\" opacity=\"0.85\"/>\n<text x=\"566\" y=\"48\" fill=\"#8b1a1a\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">-26</text>\n<text x=\"154\" y=\"76\" text-anchor=\"end\" fill=\"#a09060\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">FIFTH BLOOD EMPEROR</text>\n<rect x=\"160\" y=\"63\" width=\"400\" height=\"16\" fill=\"#8b1a1a\" opacity=\"0.85\"/>\n<text x=\"566\" y=\"76\" fill=\"#8b1a1a\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">-26</text>\n<text x=\"154\" y=\"104\" text-anchor=\"end\" fill=\"#a09060\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">Way6444</text>\n<rect x=\"160\" y=\"91\" width=\"107\" height=\"16\" fill=\"#8b1a1a\" opacity=\"0.85\"/>\n<text x=\"273\" y=\"104\" fill=\"#8b1a1a\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">-7</text>\n<text x=\"154\" y=\"132\" text-anchor=\"end\" fill=\"#a09060\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">GANGSTAR</text>\n<rect x=\"160\" y=\"119\" width=\"15\" height=\"16\" fill=\"#8b1a1a\" opacity=\"0.85\"/>\n<text x=\"181\" y=\"132\" fill=\"#8b1a1a\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">-1</text>\n<text x=\"154\" y=\"160\" text-anchor=\"end\" fill=\"#a09060\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">Grenber</text>\n<rect x=\"160\" y=\"147\" width=\"15\" height=\"16\" fill=\"#8b1a1a\" opacity=\"0.85\"/>\n<text x=\"181\" y=\"160\" fill=\"#8b1a1a\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">-1</text>\n<text x=\"154\" y=\"188\" text-anchor=\"end\" fill=\"#a09060\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">404</text>\n<rect x=\"160\" y=\"175\" width=\"15\" height=\"16\" fill=\"#8b1a1a\" opacity=\"0.85\"/>\n<text x=\"181\" y=\"188\" fill=\"#8b1a1a\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">-1</text>\n<text x=\"154\" y=\"216\" text-anchor=\"end\" fill=\"#a09060\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">jhackie</text>\n<rect x=\"160\" y=\"203\" width=\"15\" height=\"16\" fill=\"#8b1a1a\" opacity=\"0.85\"/>\n<text x=\"181\" y=\"216\" fill=\"#8b1a1a\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">-1</text>\n<text x=\"154\" y=\"244\" text-anchor=\"end\" fill=\"#a09060\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">URAL📀</text>\n<rect x=\"160\" y=\"231\" width=\"15\" height=\"16\" fill=\"#8b1a1a\" opacity=\"0.85\"/>\n<text x=\"181\" y=\"244\" fill=\"#8b1a1a\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">-1</text>\n</svg>\n\n\n<blockquote>\n<strong>⚡ Special Bulletin: The Ballad of Chiavenna's Brass-Plated Gall ⚡</strong>\n<p>Readers, your humble correspondent is compelled — <em>legally obligated by the sacred duties of sensationalist journalism</em> — to report that the audacious <strong>chiavenna</strong> has <em>once again</em> had the colossal nerve to raid none other than Donald Trump himself, making off with <strong>$500 cash, 500 weapons, and 46.96 XP</strong> in the week's single most brazen heist! This same chiavenna also personally stormed the headquarters of both <strong>jhackie</strong> and <strong>GANGSTAR</strong> on April 21st alone, dispatching two bosses before lunchtime like a man with appointments to keep and enemies to eliminate. However, fate — or perhaps the golden emperor's enforcers — extracted their toll: chiavenna's own garrison shrank by 15 units this week. Even the boldest bandit pays his tab eventually, and chiavenna's tab, dear readers, appears to be written in the ledger of a very <em>very</em> dangerous creditor.</p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<hr>\n\n<h3>WU-TANG GRINDS ON — THE OLD DRAGON REFUSES TO SLEEP!</h3>\n<span class=\"subhead\">Iron Fist Claims 29 Turfs, Settles Scores, and Stuffs His War Chest with 146 Fresh Recruits</span>\n\n<p><strong>Wu-Tang</strong>, the Iron Fist of the East Side, matched Trump blow for blow in sheer assault volume this week, launching his own 28 territorial offensives and netting <strong>29 fresh turfs</strong> to add to his already formidable eastern empire. The old dragon also personally extinguished the flickering flame of <strong>Grenber</strong> on April 24th — the second headquarters capture Wu-Tang has conducted against that unfortunate soul, a mercy only in the sense that the agony is now concluded. With 146 new gangsters joining his colours, Wu-Tang's garrison now stands at a muscular 3,801 — and every one of those boys looks hungry. The rivalry between Wu-Tang and Trump for the soul of Vendetta City shows no signs of cooling, though the leaderboard gap remains as wide as the Chicago River after a spring thaw.</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<h3>BLOOD CAPTAIN: THE CITY'S MOST RAPACIOUS BANDIT!</h3>\n<span class=\"subhead\">Seven Turfs Seized, Thirteen Raids Conducted — Who <em>Is</em> This Marauder?\n<hr>\n<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"640\" height=\"143\" style=\"font-family:Georgia,serif;background:#0a0800;display:block;margin:18px auto\">\n<text x=\"320\" y=\"22\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#c8a84a\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"bold\" letter-spacing=\"2\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">HQ RAIDS — TOP ATTACKERS</text>\n<line x1=\"20\" y1=\"30\" x2=\"620\" y2=\"30\" stroke=\"#3a2a00\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n<text x=\"148\" y=\"53\" text-anchor=\"end\" fill=\"#a09060\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">Donald Trump</text>\n<polygon points=\"156,43 161,48 156,53 151,48\" fill=\"#8b1a1a\"/>\n<rect x=\"170\" y=\"41\" width=\"410\" height=\"14\" fill=\"#6b1010\" opacity=\"0.9\" rx=\"1\"/>\n<rect x=\"577\" y=\"41\" width=\"3\" height=\"14\" fill=\"#c03030\"/>\n<text x=\"588\" y=\"53\" fill=\"#c04040\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">7✕</text>\n<text x=\"148\" y=\"82\" text-anchor=\"end\" fill=\"#a09060\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">Wu-Tang</text>\n<polygon points=\"156,72 161,77 156,82 151,77\" fill=\"#8b1a1a\"/>\n<rect x=\"170\" y=\"70\" width=\"117\" height=\"14\" fill=\"#6b1010\" opacity=\"0.9\" rx=\"1\"/>\n<rect x=\"284\" y=\"70\" width=\"3\" height=\"14\" fill=\"#c03030\"/>\n<text x=\"295\" y=\"82\" fill=\"#c04040\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">2✕</text>\n<text x=\"148\" y=\"111\" text-anchor=\"end\" fill=\"#a09060\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">chiavenna</text>\n<polygon points=\"156,101 161,106 156,111 151,106\" fill=\"#8b1a1a\"/>\n<rect x=\"170\" y=\"99\" width=\"117\" height=\"14\" fill=\"#6b1010\" opacity=\"0.9\" rx=\"1\"/>\n<rect x=\"284\" y=\"99\" width=\"3\" height=\"14\" fill=\"#c03030\"/>\n<text x=\"295\" y=\"111\" fill=\"#c04040\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">2✕</text>\n</svg>","stats":{"total_tiles_start":21418,"total_tiles_end":21470,"hq_captures":11,"raids":82,"pure_captures":60,"capture_and_raids":5,"pure_raids":17,"total_cash_looted":1290.74,"newcomers":1,"vanished":6,"top_gainer":"Donald Trump","top_gainer_net":45}}